Source: mmlib
Section: libs
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Nicolas Bourdaud <nicolas.bourdaud@mindmaze.ch>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), dh-autoreconf,
 pkg-config, gnulib, libltdl-dev, gettext, check, libgnutls-dev,
 ca-certificates-mindmaze
Standards-Version: 3.9.3
Vcs-Git: ssh://mindmaze1.epfl.ch/srv/shared/git_repositories/mmlib.git
Homepage: http://mindmaze1.epfl.ch

Package: libmmlib0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: MindMaze helper library (shared lib)
 mmlib is the general purpose library providing helper functions to other
 module. It provides facilities for logging, error reporting and basic
 geometry.
 .
 This package contains the shared library

Package: libmmlib-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libmmlib0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: MindMaze helper library (Developement files)
 mmlib is the general purpose library providing helper functions to other
 module. It provides facilities for logging, error reporting and basic
 geometry.
 .
 This package contains the files needed to compile and link programs which
 use mmlib. The manpages and examples are shipped in this package.

Package: libmmlib0-dbg
Section: debug
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libmmlib0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: MindMaze helper library (Debugging symbols)
 mmlib is the general purpose library providing helper functions to other
 module. It provides facilities for logging, error reporting and basic
 geometry.
 .
 This package provides the debugging symbols for the library.

Package: mmlib-bin
Section: utils
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: MindMaze helper library (support programs)
 mmlib is the general purpose library providing helper functions to other
 module. It provides facilities for logging, error reporting and basic
 geometry.
 .
 This package provides the support programs useful for installation or
 deployment. In particular it ships the authorization token manager program.
